video.title: Peaky Blinders
video.synopsis: A notorious gang in 1919 Birmingham, England, is led by the fierce Tommy Shelby, a crime boss set on moving up in the world no matter the cost.

episodes.synopsis: Ambitious gang leader Thomas Shelby recognizes an opportunity to move up in the world thanks to a missing crate of guns.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Thomas provokes a local kingpin by fixing a horse race and starts a war with a gypsy family; Inspector Campbell carries out a vicious raid.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Thomas schemes to get closer to Billy Kimber at the Cheltenham races, and considers an offer from IRA sympathizers to buy his stolen guns.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: As his war with the Lee family escalates, Thomas harbors suspicions about his brother's fianc√©e; Campbell pressures the gang to deliver the guns.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Thomas deals with an IRA chief bent on avenging his cousin's death; Grace must decide whether her loyalties lie with Campbell or Thomas.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Thomas prepares to oust Billy Kimber from power, but family secrets that come to light and the obsessed Campbell may prove his undoing.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: When Birmingham crime boss Tommy Shelby's beloved Garrison pub is bombed, he finds himself blackmailed into murdering an Irish dissident.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: After murdering an Irish dissident, Tommy has no choice but to be a pawn in Inspector Campbell's treacherous political game.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: After joining London crime boss Alfie Solomons in a business venture, Tommy worries that Alfie's newly revealed volatility could pose a problem.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: The Peaky Blinders take over London's Eden Club; Sabini convinces his old adversary Alfie Solomons to join forces and eradicate the gang.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: The Peaky Blinders are under attack. Tommy's power base in London is obliterated, and both Arthur and Michael are arrested and imprisoned.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Tommy plans to execute the mission given to him by Campbell: the assassination of a high-ranking member of the military establishment.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: On Tommy's wedding day, a new business partner arranges a secret transaction. Arthur has found a godly woman, and Polly meets an attractive man.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: A careless threat sparks a war. Tommy gets a rare form of payment, but his bosses flex their power to keep him in line. Polly commissions a portrait.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Tommy travels to Wales seeking absolution, and uncovers a traitor in the Economic League. Michael develops a taste for guns. Arthur gets good news.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Polly goes to confession, igniting a chain of events that reveals a trap being laid at the Shelbys' expense. Tommy plans an exit from dirty business.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Realizing he's being outmaneuvered by the Russians, Tommy seeks help from a former business partner. Polly's new friendship becomes something more.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: As Tommy prepares to commit the most audacious crime of his career, an unexpected blow forces him to face his worst fears in a race against time.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: At Christmastime 1925, members of the fractured Shelby family get word that the New York Mafia is coming to avenge murders they committed a year ago.
episodes.title: The Noose

episodes.synopsis: Reeling from their loss, the Shelbys gather in Small Heath, where Tommy calls for a family truce in order to launch an offensive against the Mafia.
episodes.title: Heathens

episodes.synopsis: Linda tries to distract Arthur, who later gets caught in an ambush. Tommy is reminded of who he was before the war. Polly meets a man from her past.
episodes.title: Blackbird

episodes.synopsis: The Mafia tries to lure one of the Shelbys into a trap. Tommy is visited by an old flame. Lizzie receives unexpected news.
episodes.title: Dangerous

episodes.synopsis: Despite being outnumbered, Tommy starts a shootout with the Mafia. Luca Changretta approaches Alfie Solomons. The British military seeks out Ada.
episodes.title: The Duel

episodes.synopsis: During the boxing match, Arthur follows a hunch. Tommy is inspired by some words of wisdom from Alfie Solomons and gets valuable intel from Jessie.
episodes.title: The Company

episodes.synopsis: Grave news from the U.S. sends the Shelbys to an urgent board meeting. Ada hides a secret. Tommy is revisited by his past, in the form of a journalist.
episodes.title: Black Tuesday

episodes.synopsis: The anonymous messages take a terrifying turn. Michael's loyalties are called into question. Tommy receives an offer from Oswald Mosley.
episodes.title: Black Cats

episodes.synopsis: Aberama heads to Glasgow to get revenge. Mosley blackmails Tommy, who decides to turn the tables on him. Frantic to find Linda, Arthur loses control.
episodes.title: Strategy

episodes.synopsis: Tommy calls a truce and meets with Jimmy McCavern. A lucrative business opportunity presents itself. Aberama is asked to put love before revenge.
episodes.title: The Loop

episodes.synopsis: At the party, Mosley makes a speech. Ben Younger faces unexpected consequences for reporting Tommy's intel on fascists. Tommy visits an asylum patient.
episodes.title: The Shock

episodes.synopsis: At a family meeting, Michael makes a bold proposal. The mole is identified. Tommy asks an old rival for help with his plan to take down Mosley.
episodes.title: Mr Jones
